{"tid":1327934,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"我去, 伟哥终于出山了","createTime":"2019-07-17T18:44:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:12:23.000Z","uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"14efd1024e26e824eabc2547657e67340dee5c3e","tid":1327934,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:44:20.000Z","msg":"终于能够再看到伟哥修鸡鸡了, 快刷一波6666666<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av59488925\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav59488925&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=53e52c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av59488925</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n技嘉刚刚推出F9 BIOS, 我贵为技嘉赌神当然要用三板斧干下去, 刷个BIOS看看<br />\n妹的, 刷好之后读不了之前留下的设定, 放在USB上也没用, 技嘉太令我失望了<br />\n不管了, 我就直接开XMP再拉到4133烧机, 坏了就寄给伟哥<br />\n<br />\n居然点亮了我操, 还能正常跑分<br />\nXMP PROFILE是C17-18-18-38, 我啥也没动就拉了频率<br />\n在HWINFO看了一下, 1.35V DDR4, 1.35V SA &amp; IO, 实际时序被技嘉自动调成20-21-21-44<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npGsQ0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpGsQ0s.png&h=ac92cbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n这是C17-18-18-38的4133<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLMgKnY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLMgKnY.png&h=d9de53f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n这是XMP+4000, 被调到19-20-20-42, 重点是还是1.35V, 打游戏都很稳定<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qebc2bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqebc2bb.png&h=cd9dd9f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4000C17 (F8)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQjqCKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQjqCKV.png&h=cc95d263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在我XMP+4133之后, 打游戏的时候就当机了, 然后又把我的系统盘搞坏了, 再也进不了系统桌面<br />\n没想到技嘉容不下我这种不学无术的赌神, 想教训我<br />\n但是我香港吴彦祖的三板斧绝活, 还是轻鬆秒杀技嘉, 成功把我的系统救回来<br />\n在这裡我就再露一手<br />\n只要反复在过了BIOS画面之后准备进系统的时候长按开机键, 就能启动系统的高级回復了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然伟哥这种硬核出山了, 再也没有我的立足之地, 我要跑路了, 拜拜"},{"pid":"ba019948f91bed94e923dc8200f58429459a4098","tid":1327934,"uid":138724,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T18:52:10.000Z","msg":"贼他妈牛B啊老铁"},{"pid":"f2b30843a995364bc335f7ae324822da43111234","tid":1327934,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"666666<br />\n大神牛逼死了"},{"pid":"bbbed54d43dd70fceb9b355ca654a624849b3de5","tid":1327934,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f2b30843a995364bc335f7ae324822da43111234","tid":1327934,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T02:10:19.000Z","msg":"666666<br />\n大神牛逼死了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:12:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/av35158629\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilibili.com%2Fvideo%2Fav35158629&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQstTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=495b6898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bilibili.com/video/av35158629</a><br />\n牛逼牛逼"}]}